reviewText: Wonderful true story of God's faithfulness to His children.  Worth your time to watch.
Amazing story of a courageous woman who chose to cling to God and his promises during her darkest days. This story will make you cry but in the end you will be blessed.

This is wonderful!  I found it educational and uplifting!!!! Thank you!
God is Good!
How can you not love these people?
Beautiful, Inspiring and wonderful. Angela's incredible story has helped restore my faith.
Halleluiah!! So many powerful testimonies! Glory to God Almighty!
